data.current_description: Searches all the IAM policies within a given accessible Resource Manager scope (project/folder/organization). This RPC gives callers especially administrators the ability to search all the IAM policies within a scope, even if they don't have `.getIamPolicy` permission of all the IAM policies. Callers should have `cloudasset.assets.searchAllIamPolicies` permission on the requested scope, otherwise the request will be rejected.
data.summary_suggestion: Search all IAM policies within a scope
data.description_suggestion: Searches all IAM policies within a given accessible Resource Manager scope (project, folder, or organization). This operation enables administrators to discover IAM policies across a scope without requiring `.getIamPolicy` permission on individual resources. Requires `cloudasset.assets.searchAllIamPolicies` permission on the requested scope. Returns a SearchAllIamPoliciesResponse containing matching IAM policies and their associated resources. Supports filtering and pagination through query parameters.

data.current_description: Searches all the resources within a given accessible Resource Manager scope (project/folder/organization). This RPC gives callers especially administrators the ability to search all the resources within a scope, even if they don't have `.get` permission of all the resources. Callers should have `cloudasset.assets.searchAllResources` permission on the requested scope, otherwise the request will be rejected.
data.summary_suggestion: Search all resources within a scope
data.description_suggestion: Searches all Google Cloud resources within a given accessible Resource Manager scope (project, folder, or organization). This operation enables administrators to discover resources across a scope without requiring `.get` permission on individual resources. Requires `cloudasset.assets.searchAllResources` permission on the requested scope. Returns a SearchAllResourcesResponse containing matching resources with their metadata, type, and location information. Supports filtering by resource type and pagination through query parameters.
